<item>
            <title>[LU-15894] Range locking in ofd is no longer needed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15894</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Range locking in ofd is no longer needed. It can unnecessarily serialize I/O under certain load.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A patch will be uploaded shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
