&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15894&quot; title=&quot;Range locking in ofd is no longer needed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15894&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15894&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ofd: revert range locking in ofd&lt;br/&gt;
